  <h1 class="headline">JPMorgan Executive Accused of Sexual Coercion — Then the Lawsuit Collapsed</h1>
  <p class="deck">A viral court filing alleged drugging, coercion, and racial harassment inside one of the world's most powerful banks. Within days, the complaint was retracted and JPMorgan called it a fabrication. Here's everything that happened.</p>
